parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "LAMMPS",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "LAMMPS",
      "Shifter",
      "SLURM",
      "MPICH"
    ],
    "resources": [
      "GPU",
      "CPU",
      "Network",
      "Storage",
      "Image: registry.nersc.gov/das/exaalt:benchmark"
    ],
    "configuration": {
      "nodes": "_NTASKS_",
      "cpus_per_task": 32,
      "gpus_per_task": 1,
      "gpu_bind": "none",
      "queue": "early_science",
      "reservation": "podman_gpu_4",
      "job_time": "00:45:00"
    },
    "environment_variables": [
      "PMI_MMAP_SYNC_WAIT_TIME=300",
      "MPICH_GPU_SUPPORT_ENABLED=1"
    ],
    "input_files": "in.run",
    "output_files": "log._NREP_",
    "commands": [
      "module purge",
      "mkdir $jobdir",
      "cp -r files/* $jobdir",
      "cd $jobdir",
      "sed -i 's/_N_/'_NREP_'/g' in.run",
      "srun shifter ./wrap.sh $exe $input -log log._NREP_"
    ]
  }
}
```
